         <abstract id="aspace_cf6282112e26f700323f4cf1a303baeb">The Lee Goebel papers contain over six hundred letters among Lee Goebel and her friends and family. The papers also include twenty-eight photographs of Goebel and her associates and information on Goebel compiled by Joel Helander.</abstract>
