      <arrangement id="aspace_2436ceb30684e4c9590289a455d8fab0">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The papers are arranged under four headings: Goebel materials compiled by Joel Helander; Correspondence; Photographs; Documents pertaining to Ralph Kirkpatrick.</p>  
      </arrangement>
